            "## Tasks\n\n- [x] Implement first.\n- [x] Implement second.\n\n"
            "## AC Priority\n\n| AC | Priority | Rationale |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| AC-1 | required | Core. |\n| AC-2 | important | Polish. |\n"
